    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in such incredible shape, it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it's practically pristine\u2014not a scratch on it and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate a car that\u2019s been kept in such top-notch, flawless condition. It\u2019s a total gem, and I can't wait for the next owner to get behind the wheel and love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
